Adrar n '''Aḍaḍ Mdni''' (s [[Tifinaɣ|tfinaɣ]] : ⴰⴷⵔⴰⵔ ⵏ ⴰⴹⴰⴹ ⵎⴰⴷⵏⵉ ; s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|tɛrabt]] : جبل أضاض مدني) iga yan udrar zɣ idrarn n [[Aṭlas mẓẓiyn|waṭlas mẓẓiyn]], tiɣzi nns tlkm 1 470 m. Illa udrar ad s 75km ɣ ugafa ɣ tsga n lqblt n tiɣrmt n [[Tiznit]], ɣ tagrawt n [[Awgnz]] ɣ tmnaḍt n [[Tamnaḍt n Actukn-Ayt Baha|Actukn-Ayt Baha]] ɣ tsga n [[Tasga n Sus-Massa|Sus-Massa]] ɣ iffus n [[Lmɣrib]].

== Aẓur n wawal ==
Ism ad n Aḍaḍ Mdni yuckad zɣ wawal anṣli s [[Taclḥit|tclḥit]] : " ''Aḍaḍ n Middn'' " acku iɣ tẓrit udrar ad zɣ yat tiɣrmt ar ak itbayyan zund ukan kra n uḍaḍ ɣayan af as gan aḍaḍ n middn. 

Illa daɣ mad ak ittinin mas aẓur n wawal ad iga-tt " ''Aḍaḍ n Lmadani'' ", ar ttinin ɣwid mas ittuymḍal yan lwaliy saliḥ ɣ afa n udrar ad ism nns ''Sidi Lmadani u Ɛli'' gmas n lwaliy saliḥ ''Sidi Iɛzza u Ɛli'' lli ituymḍal ɣ tinml n lquran n Tinzkin.

